    </para>
    <para>
     Discussion: <ulink url="https://www.pgpool.net/pipermail/pgpool-hackers/2023-January/004259.html">https://www.pgpool.net/pipermail/pgpool-hackers/2023-January/004259.html</ulink>
    </para>
   </listitem>

   <listitem>
    <!--
    2023-02-05 [ad05fa5]
    -->
    <para>
